# Team-X dev convenience env file.
#
# Copy this to `.env` (which is gitignored) and drop your Anthropic API key
# in below. On boot, if the OS keychain has no Anthropic key yet, Team-X
# will import this one into keytar ONCE and then leave the file alone —
# subsequent boots read the key from the keychain, not from here.
#
# Never commit a real key. Production users configure providers through
# the Settings UI (Phase 1 Task 37+); this file exists purely so devs can
# skip a trip through the UI on their first `pnpm dev` run.
#
# Leave any line blank to skip that key.

ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
OLLAMA_BASE_URL=http://localhost:11434
